Package com.esplibrary.packets

Class ESPPacket

java.lang.Object
com.esplibrary.packets.ESPPacket
Direct Known Subclasses:
InfDisplayData, InfV1Busy, RequestPacket, ResponseAlertData, ResponseBatteryVoltage, ResponseCurrentVolume, ResponseDataError, ResponseDataReceived, ResponseDefaultSweepDefinition, ResponseMaxSweepIndex, ResponseRequestNotProcessed, ResponseSAVVYStatus, ResponseSerialNumber, ResponseSweepDefinition, ResponseSweepSections, ResponseSweepWriteResult, ResponseUnsupported, ResponseUserBytes, ResponseVehicleSpeed, ResponseVersion, UnknownPacket
public abstract class ESPPacket extends Object
Base class for all ESPPackets. Has all the basic functionality for getting source, destination, building from a byte buffer, as well as converting an ESPPacket into a byte buffer to send to the Valentine One. Use the PacketFactory class to generate an ESPPacket of the correct type.
